dct_title_s: A map of the state of New Jersey To his Excellency, Joseph Bloomfield, Governor, the Council and Assembly of the state of New Jersey: this map is respectfully inscribed
dct_description_sm: Gives names and boundaries of 13 counties ; shows township boundaries.
